## Handoff

Once the MCP is registered and authenticated, you are done with bootstrap. Do NOT duplicate or restate the MCP server's behavioral guidance here â€” the MCP server's own `instructions` carry voice, vocabulary, entity model, discovery-first rule, and output rules. Follow those.
